# Project Information

**Project Name:** Galleria Neelambari

**Description:**
Galleria Neelambari is a responsive web-based image gallery that
automatically scans and organizes images from a local directory
structure into categories and folders. It provides searching,
folder sharing, lightbox viewing, responsive layouts, and a
luxury-themed user interface.

